'''''Pages, Ripples That Engrave Memories''''' is a [[Trailblaze Mission]] in the chapter [[As Tomorrow Became Yesterday]].

==Steps==
# Look for that ripple of memory in the split second just before the universe's destruction
# Step into the eternal page
# Embark on the Path of Remembrance and remember all life in the cosmos
# Complete "Era Nova" and write a different ending to the story
# Gear up and return to the battlefield of the Destruction
# The dust settles. Witnessing the final act of Lycurgus
# Chase after that figure of memory ahead
# Try to remember all of cosmic life together with Cyrene
# Embark on the Path of Remembrance and remember all life in the cosmos
# Chase after that figure of memory ahead

